":icon:`fa-shopping-cart`\\ （:guilabel:`購物車`）按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:97
msgid "Buy now"
msgstr "立即購買"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:99
msgid ""
"To let customers choose to go to the :ref:`review order <ecommerce/checkout/"
"review_order>` step directly, you can add an additional :guilabel:`Buy now` "
"button. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
