"以\\ :guilabel:`配置 SEPA 直接借記`\\ ，以及\\ :guilabel:`檢視其他服務商`\\ "
"。如果您使用\\ :guilabel:`Authorize.net`\\ 付款服務商，可以在同一選單中配置\\"
" :ref:`付款擷取方式 <payment_providers/manual_capture>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/payments.rst:26
msgid ""
"If you are using :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`, you "
"can also enable and configure it here."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用\\ :doc:`/applications/finance/payment_providers/paypal`\\ ，也可以"
"在此處啟用並配置它。"

