msgstr ""
"**建立新專案：**若要啟用 **Google Places API**，您首先需要建立一個專案。若要"
"執行此操作，請按一下左上角的\\ :guilabel:`選擇專案`、:guilabel:`新專案`，然後"
"按照提示設定您的專案。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Enable the Google Places API:** Go to the :guilabel:`Enabled APIs & "
"Services` and click :guilabel:`+ ENABLE APIS AND SERVICES.` Search "
"for :guilabel:`\"Places API\"` and select it. Click on "
