msgstr ""
"**啟用 Google Places API：**前往\\ :guilabel:`已啟用的 API 和服務`\\ 並按一"
"下\\ :guilabel:`+ 啟用 API 和服務`。搜尋\\ :guilabel:`「Places API」`\\ 並選"
"擇它。按一下\\ :guilabel:`「啟用」`\\ 按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:43
msgid ""
"Google's pricing depends on the number of requests and their complexity."
msgstr "Google 的定價取決於請求的數量及其複雜性。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:46
msgid "Step 2: Create API Credentials"
msgstr "步驟 2：建立 API 憑證"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to `APIs & Services --> Credentials <https://console.cloud.google.com/"
"apis/credentials>`_."
msgstr ""
"前往 `API 和服務 --> 憑證\\ <https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/"
"credentials>`_。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:50
msgid ""
"**Create credentials:** To create your credentials, go "
"to :guilabel:`Credentials`, click :guilabel:`Create Credentials`, and "
"select :guilabel:`API key`."
msgstr ""
"**建立憑證：**若要建立憑證，請前往\\ :guilabel:`憑證`，按一下\\ :guilabel:`建"
"立憑證`，然後選擇\\ :guilabel:`API 金鑰`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:54
msgid "Restrict the API Key (Optional)"
msgstr "限制 API 金鑰（選用）"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:56
msgid ""
"For security purposes, you can restrict the usage of your API key. You can "
"go to the :guilabel:`API restrictions` section to specify which APIs your "
"key can access. For the Google Places API, you can restrict it to only allow "
"requests from specific websites or apps."
msgstr ""
"出於安全考量，您可以限制 API 金鑰的使用。您可以前往\\ :guilabel:`API 限制`\\ "
"部分，指定您的金鑰可以存取哪些 API。對於 Google Places API，您可以限制它僅允"
"許來自特定網站或應用程式的請求。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:61
msgid "Save Your API Key: copy your API key and securely store it."
msgstr "儲存您的 API 金鑰：複製您的 API 金鑰並安全地儲存它。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/address_autocomplete.rst:62
msgid "Do not share it publicly or expose it in client-side code."
msgstr "請勿公開分享或在客戶端程式碼中暴露它。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:3
msgid "Set up a content delivery network (CDN)"
msgstr "設定內容傳遞網路（CDN）"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:8
msgid "Deploying with KeyCDN"
msgstr "使用 KeyCDN 部署"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:10
msgid ""
"A :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` or *content distribution network*, "
"is a geographically distributed network of servers that provides high speed "
"internet content. The :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` provides quick, "
"high-quality content delivery for content-heavy websites."
msgstr ""
"\\ :abbr:`CDN（Content Delivery Network）`\\ 或\\ *內容分發網路*\\ 是一個地理"
"分散的伺服器網路，提供高速網際網路內容。\\ :abbr:`CDN（Content Delivery "
"Network）`\\ 為內容密集型網站提供快速、高品質的內容傳遞。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:14
msgid ""
"This document will guide you through the setup of a KeyCDN_ account with an "
"Odoo powered website."
msgstr "本文件將指導您使用 Odoo 驅動的網站設定 KeyCDN_ 帳戶。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:17
msgid "Create a pull zone in the KeyCDN dashboard"
msgstr "在 KeyCDN Dashboard 中建立拉取區域"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:19
msgid ""
"On the KeyCDN dashboard, start by navigating to the :menuselection:`Zones` "
"menu item on the left. On the form, give a value to the :guilabel:`Zone "
"Name`, which will appear as part of the :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery "
"Network)`'s :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)`. Then, set "
"the :guilabel:`Zone Status` to :guilabel:`active` to engage the zone. For "
"the :guilabel:`Zone Type` set the value to :guilabel:`Pull`, and then, "
"finally, under the :guilabel:`Pull Settings`, enter the :guilabel:`Origin "
"URL`— this address should be the full Odoo database :abbr:`URL (Uniform "
"Resource Locator)`."
msgstr ""
"在 KeyCDN Dashboard 中，首先前往左側的\\ :menuselection:`Zones`\\ 選單項目。"
"在表單中，為\\ :guilabel:`Zone Name`\\ 設定一個值，該值將作為\\ :abbr:`CDN（"
"Content Delivery Network）`\\ 的\\ :abbr:`URL（Uniform Resource Locator）`\\ "
"的一部分顯示。然後，將\\ :guilabel:`Zone Status`\\ 設定為\\ "
":guilabel:`active`\\ 以啟用該區域。對於\\ :guilabel:`Zone Type`\\ 將值設定"
"為\\ :guilabel:`Pull`\\ ，最後，在\\ :guilabel:`Pull Settings`\\ 下，輸入\\ "
":guilabel:`Origin URL`\\ — 此網址應為完整的 Odoo 資料庫\\ :abbr:`URL（"
"Uniform Resource Locator）`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:28
msgid ""
"Use ``https://yourdatabase.odoo.com`` and replace the *yourdatabase* "
"subdomain prefix with the actual name of the database. A custom :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` can be used, as well, in place of the Odoo "
"subdomain that was provided to the database."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``https://yourdatabase.odoo.com`` 並將 *yourdatabase* 子網域前綴替換為資"
"料庫的實際名稱。也可以使用自訂的\\ :abbr:`URL（Uniform Resource Locator）`\\ "
"來取代提供給資料庫的 Odoo 子網域。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "KeyCDN's Zone configuration page."
msgstr "KeyCDN 的區域配置頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:36
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`General Settings` heading below the zone form, click "
"the :guilabel:`Show all settings` button to expand the zone options. This "
"should be the last option on the page. After expanding "
"the :guilabel:`General Settings` ensure that the :guilabel:`CORS` option "
"is :guilabel:`enabled`."
msgstr ""
"在區域表單下方的\\ :guilabel:`General Settings`\\ 標題下，按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`Show all settings`\\ 按鈕以展開區域選項。這應該是頁面上的最後一個"
"選項。展開\\ :guilabel:`General Settings`\\ 後，確保\\ :guilabel:`CORS`\\ 選"
"項已\\ :guilabel:`enabled`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:41
msgid ""
"Next, scroll to the bottom of the zone configuration page "
"and :guilabel:`Save` the changes. KeyCDN will indicate that the new zone "
"will be deployed. This can take about 10 minutes."
msgstr ""
"接下來，捲動到區域配置頁面底部並\\ :guilabel:`Save`\\ 變更。KeyCDN 將指示新區"
"域將被部署。這可能需要約 10 分鐘。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "KeyCDN deploying the new Zone."
msgstr "KeyCDN 正在部署新的區域。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:49
msgid ""
"A new :guilabel:`Zone URL` has been generated for your Zone, in this example "
"it is ``pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com``. This value will differ for each database."
msgstr ""
"已為您的區域生成新的\\ :guilabel:`Zone URL`\\ ，在此範例中為 ``pulltest-"
"xxxxx.kxcdn.com``。此值對於每個資料庫都會不同。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:52
msgid ""
"Copy this :guilabel:`Zone URL` to a text editor for later, as it will be "
"used in the next steps."
msgstr ""
"將此\\ :guilabel:`Zone URL`\\ 複製到文字編輯器中以供稍後使用，因為它將在下一"
"步中使用。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:55
msgid "Configure the Odoo instance with the new zone"
msgstr "使用新區域配置 Odoo 實例"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:57
msgid ""
"In the Odoo :guilabel:`Website` app, go to the :menuselection:`Settings` and "
"then activate the :guilabel:`Content Delivery Network (CDN)` setting and "
"copy/paste the :guilabel:`Zone URL` value from the earlier step into "
"the :guilabel:`CDN Base URL` field. This field is only visible and "
"configurable when the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` is activated."
msgstr ""
"在 Odoo\\ :guilabel:`網站`\\ 應用程式中，前往\\ :menuselection:`Settings`\\ "
"，然後啟用\\ :guilabel:`Content Delivery Network (CDN)`\\ 設定，並將先前步驟"
"中的\\ :guilabel:`Zone URL`\\ 值複製/貼上到\\ :guilabel:`CDN Base URL`\\ 欄位"
"中。此欄位僅在啟用\\ :ref:`開發者模式 <developer-mode>`\\ 時可見和可配置。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:63
msgid ""
"Ensure that there are two *forward slashes* (`//`) before the :guilabel:`CDN "
"Base URL` and one forward slash (`/`) after the :guilabel:`CDN Base URL`."
msgstr ""
"確保在\\ :guilabel:`CDN Base URL`\\ 之前有兩個\\ *正斜線*\\ （``//``），並"
"在\\ :guilabel:`CDN Base URL`\\ 之後有一個正斜線（``/``）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:66
msgid ":guilabel:`Save` the settings when complete."
msgstr "完成後\\ :guilabel:`Save`\\ 設定。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "Activate the CDN setting in Odoo."
msgstr "在 Odoo 中啟用 CDN 設定。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:72
msgid ""
"Now the website is using the CDN for the resources matching "
"the :guilabel:`CDN filters` regular expressions."
msgstr "目前網站針對符合\\ :guilabel:`CDN 篩選條件`\\ 正規表示式的資源使用 CDN。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:75
msgid ""
"In the HTML of the Odoo website, the :abbr:`CDN (content delivery network)` "
"integration is evidenced as working properly by checking the :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locators)` of images. The *CDN Base URL* value can be seen "
"by using your web browser's :guilabel:`Inspect` feature on the Odoo website. "
"Look for it's record by searching within the :guilabel:`Network` tab inside "
"of devtools."
msgstr ""
"在 Odoo 網站的 HTML 中，可透過檢查圖片的\\ :abbr:`URL（統一資源定位器）`\\ 來"
"驗證\\ :abbr:`CDN（內容傳遞網路）`\\ 整合是否正常運作。使用網頁瀏覽器的\\ "
":guilabel:`檢查`\\ 功能檢視 Odoo 網站，可看到 *CDN 基礎網址*值。可在開發者工"
"具的\\ :guilabel:`網路`\\ 分頁中搜尋其記錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid ""
"The CDN Base URL can be seen using the inspect function on the Odoo website."
msgstr "可使用 Odoo 網站的檢查功能查看 CDN 基礎網址。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:85
msgid ""
"Prevent security issues by activating cross-origin resource sharing (CORS)"
msgstr "啟用跨來源資源共用（CORS）以防止安全性問題"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:87
msgid ""
"A security restriction in some browsers (such as Mozilla Firefox and Google "
"Chrome) prevents a remotely linked CSS file to fetch relative resources on "
"this same external server."
msgstr ""
"某些瀏覽器（例如 Mozilla Firefox 和 Google Chrome）的安全性限制會阻止遠端連結"
"的 CSS 檔案擷取同一外部伺服器上的相對資源。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:90
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)` option isn't enabled in "
"the :guilabel:`CDN Zone`, the more obvious resulting problem on a standard "
"Odoo website will be the lack of *Font Awesome* icons because the font file "
"declared in the *Font Awesome* CSS won't be loaded from the remote server."
msgstr ""
"如果在\\ :guilabel:`CDN 區域`\\ 中未啟用\\ :abbr:`CORS（跨來源資源共用）`\\ "
"選項，標準 Odoo 網站上較明顯的問題會是缺少 *Font Awesome* 圖示，因為 *Font "
"Awesome* CSS 中宣告的字型檔案無法從遠端伺服器載入。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:95
msgid ""
"When these cross-origin resource issues occur, a security error message "
"similar to the output below will appear in the web browser's developer "
"console:"
msgstr ""
"當這些跨來源資源問題發生時，網頁瀏覽器的開發者主控台中會出現類似以下輸出的安"
"全性錯誤訊息："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:98
msgid ""
"``Font from origin 'http://pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com' has been blocked from "
"loading /shop:1 by Cross-Origin Resource Sharing policy: No 'Access-Control-"
"Allow-Origin' header is present on the requested resource. Origin 'http://"
"yourdatabase.odoo.com' is therefore not allowed access.``"
msgstr ""
"``Font from origin 'http://pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com' has been blocked from "
"loading /shop:1 by Cross-Origin Resource Sharing policy: No 'Access-Control-"
"Allow-Origin' header is present on the requested resource. Origin 'http://"
"yourdatabase.odoo.com' is therefore not allowed access.``"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "Error message populated in the browser console."
msgstr "瀏覽器主控台中顯示的錯誤訊息。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:106
msgid ""
"Enabling the :abbr:`CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)` option in "
"the :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` settings fixes this issue."
msgstr ""
"在\\ :abbr:`CDN（內容傳遞網路）`\\ 設定中啟用\\ :abbr:`CORS（跨來源資源共用"
"）`\\ 選項可修正此問題。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:3
msgid "Cookies bar"
msgstr "Cookie 橫幅"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Cookies** are small text files sent to your device when you visit a "
"website. They are processed and stored by your browser and record visitor "
"information like login details, preferences, and browsing history. "
"**Essential cookies** are necessary for the website to function, while "
"**optional cookies** are used to analyze behavior or display ads."
msgstr ""
"**Cookie**\\ 是您造訪網站時傳送到您裝置的小型文字檔。它們由您的瀏覽器處理和儲"
"存，並記錄訪客資訊，如登入詳細資料、偏好設定和瀏覽記錄。**必要 Cookie**\\ 是"
"網站運作所必需的,而\\ **選用 Cookie**\\ 則用於分析行為或顯示廣告。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:10
msgid ""
"Data protection laws require notifying visitors about data collection "
"methods and purposes. **Cookies bar** fulfill this obligation by informing "
"visitors on their first visit and allowing them to decide whether to store "
"all or only essential cookies on their device."
msgstr ""
"資料保護法要求通知訪客資料收集的方法和目的。**Cookie 提示列**\\ 透過在訪客首"
"次造訪時通知他們並允許他們決定是否在其裝置上儲存所有或僅必要的 Cookie 來履行"
"此義務。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:15
msgid ""
"Cookies bars are required to obtain visitors' consent for optional cookies "
"only. Consent is not required for essential cookies."
msgstr "Cookie 提示列僅需要獲得訪客對選用 Cookie 的同意。必要 Cookie 不需要同意。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:18
msgid ""
"Odoo is compliant with `Google consent mode v2 <https://support.google.com/"
"tagmanager/answer/13695607>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 符合\\ `Google 同意模式 v2 <https://support.google.com/tagmanager/"
"answer/13695607>`_\\ 規範。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:23
msgid ""
"To add a cookies bar on your website, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and enable :guilabel:`Cookies Bar` in "
"the :guilabel:`Privacy` section. This activates :guilabel:`Block tracking "
"3rd-party services` by default, including social media, video hosting "
"platforms, and Google services. Click :guilabel:`Add domains to the block "
"list` to include other external websites. These services remain blocked on "
"your website until visitors accept optional cookies."
msgstr ""
"若要在您的網站上加入 Cookie 列，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 配置 --> 設"
"定`\\ ，並在\\ :guilabel:`隱私`\\ 區段中啟用\\ :guilabel:`Cookie 列`\\ 。這會"
"預設啟用\\ :guilabel:`封鎖追蹤第三方服務`\\ ，包括社交媒體、影片託管平台和 "
"Google 服務。按一下\\ :guilabel:`將網域加入封鎖清單`\\ 以包含其他外部網站。這"
"些服務在您的網站上保持封鎖狀態，直到訪客接受選用的 Cookie。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:31
msgid ""
"Using third-party cookies without a cookies bar does not prevent them from "
"being triggered. Only the presence of a cookie bar **and** the visitor’s "
"refusal ensure that these cookies are blocked."
msgstr ""
"使用第三方 Cookie 而不使用 Cookie 欄並不會阻止它們被觸發。只有 Cookie 欄的存"
"在**以及**訪客的拒絕才能確保這些 Cookie 被封鎖。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:37
msgid "Cookies policy"
msgstr "Cookie 政策"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:39
msgid ""
"When you enable the cookies bar for your website, Odoo creates the **Cookie "
"Policy** page (`/cookie-policy`) containing a list of cookies set by "
"default, with their purpose and examples."
msgstr ""
"當您為網站啟用 Cookie 欄時，Odoo 會建立\\ **Cookie 政策**\\ 頁面（`/cookie-"
"policy`），其中包含預設設定的 Cookie 清單及其用途和範例。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:48
msgid "Category"
msgstr "類別"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:49
msgid "Role"
msgstr "角色"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:50
msgid "Name"
msgstr "名稱"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:51
msgid "Essential - Session & Security"
msgstr "必要 - 工作階段與安全性"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:52
msgid ""
"Authenticate visitors, protect visitor data and allow the website to deliver "
"the services visitors expects, such as maintaining the content of their "
"cart, or allowing file uploads. The website will not work properly without "
"these cookies."
msgstr ""
"驗證訪客、保護訪客資料並允許網站提供訪客期望的服務，例如維護購物車內容或允許"
"檔案上傳。沒有這些 Cookie，網站將無法正常運作。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:55
msgid "session_id (Odoo)"
msgstr "session_id（Odoo）"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:56
msgid "Essential - Preferences"
msgstr "必要 - 偏好設定"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:57
msgid ""
"Remember information about the preferred look or behavior of the website, "
"such as the preferred language or region. The website will continue to "
"function without these cookies, but the visitor’s experience may be affected."
msgstr ""
"記住有關網站外觀或行為偏好的資訊，例如偏好的語言或地區。沒有這些 Cookie，網站"
"將繼續運作，但訪客體驗可能會受到影響。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:60
msgid "frontend_lang (Odoo)"
msgstr "frontend_lang (Odoo)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:61
msgid "Optional - Interaction History"
msgstr "選用 - 互動歷史記錄"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:62
msgid ""
"Collect information about your interactions with the website, the pages "
"you've seen, and any specific marketing campaign that brought you to the "
"website. The website will work without these cookies, but some features or "
"services may not perform optimally."
msgstr ""
"收集有關您與網站互動的資訊、您瀏覽過的頁面以及將您帶到網站的任何特定行銷活動"
"。沒有這些 Cookie，網站仍可運作，但某些功能或服務可能無法達到最佳效能。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:65
msgid ""
"im_livechat_previous_operator (Odoo), utm_campaign (Odoo), utm_source "
"(Odoo), utm_medium (Odoo)"
msgstr ""
"im_livechat_previous_operator（Odoo）、utm_campaign（Odoo）、utm_source（Odoo"
"）、utm_medium（Odoo）"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:69
msgid "Optional - Advertising & Marketing"
msgstr "選用 - 廣告與行銷"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:70
msgid ""
"Make advertising more engaging to visitors and more valuable to publishers "
"and advertisers, such as providing more relevant ads when you visit other "
"websites that display ads or to improve reporting on ad campaign "
"performance. Note that some third-party services may install additional "
"cookies on your browser in order to identify you."
msgstr ""
"使廣告對訪客更具吸引力，對發佈者和廣告商更有價值，例如在您造訪其他顯示廣告的"
"網站時提供更相關的廣告，或改善廣告活動效能報告。請注意，某些第三方服務可能會"
"在您的瀏覽器上安裝其他 Cookie 以識別您的身分。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:74
msgid "__gads (Google), __gac (Google)"
msgstr "__gads（Google）、__gac（Google）"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:76
msgid "Optional - Analytics"
msgstr "選用 - 分析"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:77
msgid ""
"Understand how visitors engage with the website, via Google Analytics. The "
"website will still work without these cookies."
msgstr "透過 Google Analytics 瞭解訪客如何與網站互動。沒有這些 Cookie，網站仍可運作。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:79
msgid "_ga (Google), _gat (Google), _gid (Google), _gac_* (Google)"
msgstr "_ga（Google）、_gat（Google）、_gid（Google）、_gac_*（Google）"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:85
msgid ""
"It is not possible to let visitors customize or select which optional "
"cookies they want to allow."
msgstr "無法讓訪客自訂或選擇他們想要允許的選用 Cookie。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:88
msgid ""
"You could add a link to this page in your website's footer, for example."
msgstr "您可以在網站頁尾加入此頁面的連結。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:93
msgid "Edit the Cookies policy page"
msgstr "編輯 Cookie 政策頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:95
msgid ""
"To access it, click the :guilabel:`Cookie Policy` hyperlink in the cookies "
"bar or open the page from :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."
msgstr ""
"若要存取該頁面，請按一下 Cookie 欄中的\\ :guilabel:`Cookie 政策`\\ 超連結，或"
"從\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 網站 --> 頁面`\\ 開啟該頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:98
msgid ""
"To adapt the content of the page according to your needs, click "
"the :guilabel:`Edit` button."
msgstr "若要根據您的需求調整頁面內容，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`編輯`\\ 按鈕。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:101
msgid ""
"You have to list every cookie you added yourself on the `/cookie-policy` "
"page including their name, role, category and duration."
msgstr ""
"您必須在 `/cookie-policy` 頁面上列出您自己加入的每個 Cookie，包括其名稱、角色"
"、類別和持續時間。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:105
msgid "To check the duration of cookies, use your browser’s developer tools."
msgstr "若要檢查 cookie 的持續時間，請使用瀏覽器的開發者工具。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:108
msgid ":doc:`Pages <../structure/pages>`"
msgstr ":doc:`頁面 <../structure/pages>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:113
msgid "Customization"
msgstr "自訂"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:115
msgid ""
"To adapt the display of the cookies bar on your website, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` on the website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Invisible "
"Elements` section at the bottom of the panel, and click :guilabel:`Cookies "
"Bar`. You can modify the :guilabel:`Layout` and :guilabel:`Size` of the "
"cookies bar, and enable :guilabel:`Backdrop` to gray out the page in the "
"background when the cookies bar is displayed on the screen."
msgstr ""
"若要調整網站上 cookie 列的顯示，請在網站編輯器上按一下\\ :guilabel:`編輯`\\ "
"，前往面板底部的\\ :guilabel:`隱藏元素`\\ 區段，然後按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`Cookie 列`\\ 。您可以修改 cookie 列的\\ :guilabel:`版面配置`\\ "
"和\\ :guilabel:`大小`\\ ，並啟用\\ :guilabel:`背景`\\ 以在螢幕上顯示 cookie "
"列時將背景頁面變灰。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:121
msgid ""
"Click anywhere in the building block to further customize the appearance of "
"the cookies bar using :guilabel:`Block`, :guilabel:`Column` and/"
"or :guilabel:`Inline Text` customization options."
msgstr ""
"按一下建構區塊中的任何位置，以使用\\ :guilabel:`區塊`\\ 、:guilabel:`欄位`\\ "
"及／或\\ :guilabel:`行內文字`\\ 自訂選項進一步自訂 Cookie 橫幅的外觀。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:124
msgid ""
"To edit the contents of the cookies bar (i.e., the consent message), click "
"directly in the building block."
msgstr "若要編輯 Cookie 橫幅的內容（例如同意訊息），請直接按一下建構區塊。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:3
msgid "Domain names"
msgstr "網域名稱"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:5
msgid ""
"Domain names are text-based addresses identifying online locations, such as "
"websites. They provide a more memorable and recognizable way for people to "
"navigate the internet than numerical IP addresses."
msgstr ""
"網域名稱是識別線上位置（例如網站）的文字式地址。與數字 IP 地址相比，它們為人"
"們提供了一種更容易記憶和識別的網際網路瀏覽方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:8
msgid ""
"**Odoo Online** and **Odoo.sh** databases use a **subdomain** of the "
"`odoo.com` **domain** by default (e.g., `mycompany.odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo 雲端版**與\\ **Odoo.sh**\\ 資料庫預設使用\\ `odoo.com` **網域**的**子"
"網域**（例如\\ `mycompany.odoo.com`）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:11
msgid ""
"However, you can use a custom domain name instead by :ref:`registering a "
"free domain name <domain-name/register>` (only available for Odoo Online "
"databases) or by :ref:`configuring a domain name you already own <domain-"
"name/existing>`."
msgstr ""
"不過，您可以透過\\ :ref:`註冊免費網域名稱 <domain-name/register>`（僅適用於 "
"Odoo 雲端版資料庫）或\\ :ref:`配置您已擁有的網域名稱 <domain-name/existing>"
"`\\ 來使用自訂網域名稱。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:16
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorials: Register a free domain name [video] <https://www.odoo.com/"
"slides/slide/register-a-free-domain-name-1663>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo 教學：註冊免費網域名稱 [影片] <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"register-a-free-domain-name-1663>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:18
msgid ""
"`Magic Sheet - Website domain configuration [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/"
"drive/folders/1sXbp7sC6TKG2v-8hcRAMhA6ftKmRxba_>`_"
msgstr ""
"`精妙筆記 - 網站網域配置 [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/"
"1sXbp7sC6TKG2v-8hcRAMhA6ftKmRxba_>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:24
msgid "Register a free domain name with Odoo"
msgstr "使用 Odoo 註冊免費網域名稱"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:26
msgid ""
"To register a one-year free domain name for your Odoo Online database, sign "
"in to your account and go to the `database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/"
"databases>`_. Click the :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`gear`) button next to "
"the database name and select :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Domain Names`."
msgstr ""
"若要為您的 Odoo 雲端版資料庫註冊一年期免費網域名稱，請登入您的帳戶並前往\\ "
"`資料庫管理器 <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_。按一下資料庫名稱旁的\\ "
":icon:`fa-gear`（:guilabel:`齒輪`）按鈕，然後選擇\\ :icon:`fa-globe` "
":guilabel:`網域名稱`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:None
msgid "Accessing a database's domain names configuration"
msgstr "存取資料庫的網域名稱配置"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:34
msgid "Search for the desired domain name and check its availability."
msgstr "搜尋所需的網域名稱並檢查其可用性。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:None
msgid "Searching for an available domain name"
msgstr "搜尋可用的網域名稱"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:40
msgid ""
"Ensure the Website app is installed if the domain name registration option "
"does not appear."
msgstr "如果網域名稱註冊選項未出現，請確保已安裝網站應用程式。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:42
msgid ""
"Select the desired domain name, fill in the :guilabel:`Domain Owner` form, "
"and click :guilabel:`Register`. The chosen domain name is directly linked to "
"the database."
msgstr ""
"選擇所需的網域名稱，填寫\\ :guilabel:`網域擁有者`\\ 表單，然後按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`註冊`。所選的網域名稱會直接連結至該資料庫。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:None
msgid "Filling in the domain owner information"
msgstr "填寫網域擁有者資訊"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:48
msgid ""
"Next, you should :ref:`map your domain name to your Odoo website <domain-"
"name/website-map>`."
msgstr ""
"接下來，您應該\\ :ref:`將網域名稱對應至您的 Odoo 網站 <domain-name/website-"
"map>`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:51
msgid ""
"A verification email from `noreply@domainnameverification.net` will be sent "
"to the email address provided in the :guilabel:`Domain Owner` form. It is "
"essential to verify your email address to keep the domain active and receive "
"the renewal quote before expiration."
msgstr ""
"來自\\ `noreply@domainnameverification.net`\\ 的驗證電子郵件將傳送至\\ "
":guilabel:`網域擁有者`\\ 表單中提供的電子郵件地址。驗證您的電子郵件地址對於保"
"持網域活躍狀態並在到期前收到續約報價至關重要。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:55
msgid ""
"The domain name registration is free for the first year. After this period, "
"Odoo will continue to manage the domain in partnership with **Gandi.net**, "
"the domain name registrar, and you will be charged `Gandi.net's renewal rate "
"<https://www.gandi.net/en/domain>`_. Odoo sends a renewal quotation every "
"year to the email address mentioned in the :guilabel:`Domain Owner` form "
"several weeks before the expiration date of the domain. The domain is "
"renewed automatically when the quotation is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"網域名稱註冊第一年免費。在此期間之後，Odoo 將與網域名稱註冊商\\ "
"**Gandi.net**\\ 合作繼續管理該網域，您將被收取\\ `Gandi.net 的續約費率 "
"<https://www.gandi.net/en/domain>`_。Odoo 每年會在網域到期日前數週將續約報價"
"傳送至\\ :guilabel:`網域擁有者`\\ 表單中提及的電子郵件地址。當報價獲得確認時"
"，該網域將自動續約。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:63
msgid "The offer is only available for **Odoo Online** databases."
msgstr "此優惠僅適用於 **Odoo 雲端版**資料庫。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:64
msgid "The offer is limited to **one** domain name per client."
msgstr "此優惠每位客戶限定**一個**網域名稱。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:65
msgid "The offer is limited to the registration of a **new** domain name."
msgstr "此優惠僅限註冊**新**網域名稱。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:66
msgid ""
"The offer is available to *One App Free* plans. Ensure that your website "
"contains enough original content for Odoo to verify that your request is "
"legitimate and respects `Odoo's Acceptable Use Policy <https://www.odoo.com/"
"acceptable-use>`_. Given the high number of requests, it can take Odoo "
"several days to review them."
msgstr ""
"此優惠適用於\\ *單一應用程式免費*\\ 方案。請確保您的網站包含足夠的原創內容，"
"以便 Odoo 驗證您的請求合法且符合\\ `Odoo 的可接受使用政策 <https://"
"www.odoo.com/acceptable-use>`_。鑑於請求數量眾多，Odoo 可能需要數天時間來審查"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:74
msgid "DNS records"
msgstr "DNS 記錄"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:76
msgid ""
"To manage your free domain name :abbr:`DNS (domain name system)` records, "
"open the `database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_, click "
"the :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`gear`) button next to the database name, "
"select :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Domain Names`, and click :guilabel:`DNS`."
msgstr ""
"若要管理您的免費網域名稱\\ :abbr:`DNS（網域名稱系統）`\\ 記錄，請開啟\\ `資料"
"庫管理器 <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_，按一下資料庫名稱旁的\\ "
":icon:`fa-gear`（:guilabel:`齒輪`）按鈕，選擇\\ :icon:`fa-globe` "
":guilabel:`網域名稱`，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`DNS`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`A`: the A record holds the IP address of the domain. It is "
"automatically created and **cannot** be edited or deleted."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`A`\\ ：A 記錄儲存網域的 IP 位址。它會自動建立且\\ **無法**\\ 編"
"輯或刪除。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`CNAME`: CNAME records forward one domain or subdomain to another "
"domain. One is automatically created to map the `www.` subdomain to the "
"database. If the database is renamed, the CNAME record **must** also be "
"renamed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`CNAME`：CNAME 記錄將一個網域或子網域轉發至另一個網域。系統會自動建"
"立一個記錄，將\\ `www.`\\ 子網域對應至資料庫。如果資料庫重新命名，CNAME 記"
"錄**也必須**重新命名。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:85
msgid ":guilabel:`MX`: MX records instruct servers on where to deliver emails."
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`MX`\\ ：MX 記錄會指示伺服器將電子郵件傳送到哪裡。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`TXT`: TXT records can be used for different purposes (e.g., to "
"verify domain name ownership)."
msgstr ":guilabel:`TXT`：TXT 記錄可用於不同目的（例如驗證網域名稱所有權）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:89
msgid ""
"Any modification to the DNS records can take up to **72 hours** to propagate "
"worldwide on all servers."
msgstr ""
"對 DNS 記錄的任何修改可能需要最多\\ **72 小時**\\ 才能在全球所有伺服器上傳播"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:93
msgid ""
"`Contact Odoo support <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ if you need assistance "
"to manage your domain name."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要協助管理網域名稱，請\\ `聯絡 Odoo 支援 <https://www.odoo.com/help>"
"`_。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:97
msgid "Mailbox"
msgstr "郵箱"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:99
msgid ""
"The one-year free domain name offer does **not** include a mailbox. There "
"are two options to link your domain name with a mailbox."
msgstr ""
"一年免費網域名稱方案\\ **不**\\ 包含郵箱。有兩種方式可將您的網域名稱與郵箱連"
"結。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:103
msgid "Use a subdomain"
msgstr "使用子網域"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:105
msgid ""
"You can create a subdomain (e.g., `subdomain.yourdomain.com`) to use as an "
"alias domain for the database. It allows users to create records in the "
"database from emails received on their `email@subdomain.yourdomain.com` "
"alias."
msgstr ""
"您可以建立子網域（例如 `subdomain.yourdomain.com`）作為資料庫的別名網域。這樣"
"可讓使用者從其 `email@subdomain.yourdomain.com` 別名接收的電子郵件中在資料庫"
"建立記錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:109
msgid ""
"To do so, open the `database manager <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>`_, "
"click the :icon:`fa-gear` (:guilabel:`gear`) button next to the database "
"name and select :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`Domain Names`. "
"Click :guilabel:`DNS`, then :guilabel:`Add DNS record` and "
"select :guilabel:`CNAME`. Next, enter the desired subdomain in "
"the :guilabel:`Name` field (e.g., `subdomain`), the original database domain "
"with a period at the end (e.g., `mycompany.odoo.com.`) in "
"the :guilabel:`Content` field, and click :guilabel:`Add record`."
msgstr ""
"若要執行此操作，請開啟\\ `資料庫管理員 <https://www.odoo.com/my/databases>"
"`_，按一下資料庫名稱旁邊的\\ :icon:`fa-gear`（:guilabel:`齒輪`）按鈕，然後選"
"取\\ :icon:`fa-globe` :guilabel:`網域名稱`。按一下\\ :guilabel:`DNS`，然後按"
"一下\\ :guilabel:`加入 DNS 記錄`，選取\\ :guilabel:`CNAME`。接下來，在\\ "
":guilabel:`名稱`\\ 欄位中輸入所需的子網域（例如 `subdomain`），在\\ "
":guilabel:`內容`\\ 欄位中輸入原始資料庫網域並在結尾加上句點（例如 "
"`mycompany.odoo.com.`），然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`加入記錄`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:116
msgid ""
"Then, add the alias domain as your *own domain* by clicking :guilabel:`Use "
