msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`公開`\\ ：所有人都可以存取該頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:113
msgid ":guilabel:`Signed In`: Only signed-in users can access the page."
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`已登入`\\ ：僅已登入使用者可以存取該頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Restricted Group`: Select the :doc:`user access group(s) </"
"applications/general/users/access_rights>` in the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"group` field."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`受限群組`\\ ：在\\ :guilabel:`授權群組`\\ 欄位中選擇\\ :doc:`使"
"用者存取群組 </applications/general/users/access_rights>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:116
msgid ""
":guilabel:`With Password`: Type the password required to access the page in "
"the :guilabel:`Password` field."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`需要密碼`\\ ：在\\ :guilabel:`密碼`\\ 欄位中輸入存取該頁面所需"
"的密碼。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is a template`: Toggle the switch to save the page as a template "
"and add it to the :guilabel:`Custom`  category."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`作為範本`\\ ：切換開關以將頁面儲存為範本，並將其加入\\ "
":guilabel:`自訂`\\ 類別。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:123
msgid ""
"*Some* of these properties can also be modified in batch "
"from :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."
msgstr ""
"其中\\ *部分*\\ 屬性也可以從\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 網站 --> 頁面`\\ 批次"
"修改。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:129
msgid "Duplicating pages"
msgstr "複製頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:131
msgid ""
"To duplicate a page, access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, and click :guilabel:`Duplicate Page`. Enter a :guilabel:`Page "
"Name`, then click :guilabel:`OK`. By default, the new page is added after "
"the duplicated page in the menu, but you can remove it from the menu or "
"change its position using the :doc:`menu editor <header_footer>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:139
msgid "Deleting pages"
msgstr "刪除頁面"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:141
msgid "To delete a page, proceed as follows:"
msgstr "若要刪除頁面，請依照以下步驟操作："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:143
msgid ""
"Access the page, then go to :menuselection:`Site --> Properties` and "
"click :guilabel:`Delete Page`."
msgstr ""
"存取該頁面，然後前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 屬性`\\ 並按一下\\ "
":guilabel:`刪除頁面`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:144
msgid ""
"A pop-up window shows all links referring to the page you want to delete, "
"organized by category. To ensure website visitors don't land on an error "
"page, you must update all the links on your website referring to the page. "
"To do so, expand a category, then click on a link to open it in a new "
"window. Alternatively, you can set up a :ref:`redirection <website/pages/URL-"
"redirection>` for the deleted page."
msgstr ""
"彈出視窗會顯示所有參照到您要刪除之頁面的連結，並依類別組織。為確保網站訪客不"
"會進入錯誤頁面，您必須更新網站上所有參照到該頁面的連結。若要執行此操作，請展"
"開類別，然後按一下連結以在新視窗中開啟。或者，您也可以為已刪除的頁面設定\\ "
":ref:`重新導向 <website/pages/URL-redirection>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:149
msgid ""
"Once you have updated the links (or set up a :ref:`redirection <website/"
"pages/URL-redirection>`), tick the :guilabel:`I am sure about this` check "
"box, then click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr ""
"更新連結（或設定\\ :ref:`重新導向 <website/pages/URL-redirection>`\\ ）後，勾"
"選\\ :guilabel:`我確定要執行此操作`\\ 核取方塊，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`確"
"定`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:155
msgid "URL redirect mapping"
msgstr "網址重新導向對應"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:157
msgid ""
"URL redirect mapping consists in sending visitors and search engines to a "
"URL different from the one they initially requested. This technique is used, "
"for example, to prevent broken links when you :ref:`delete a page <website/"
"pages/delete-page>`, :ref:`modify its URL <website/pages/page_properties>`, "
"or migrate your site from another platform to an Odoo :doc:`domain <../"
"configuration/domain_names>`. It can also be used to improve :doc:`seo`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:163
msgid ""
"To access existing URL redirections and create new ones, :doc:`activate the "
"developer mode </applications/general/developer_mode>` and go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Redirects`."
msgstr ""
"若要存取現有的網址重新導向並建立新的重新導向，請\\ :doc:`啟用開發者模式 </"
"applications/general/developer_mode>`\\ ，然後前往\\ :menuselection:`網"
"站 --> 配置 --> 重新導向`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:168
msgid ""
"A redirect record is added automatically every time you :ref:`modify a "
"page's URL <website/pages/page_properties>` and enable :guilabel:`Redirect "
"Old URL`."
msgstr ""
"每次\\ :ref:`修改頁面網址 <website/pages/page_properties>`\\ 並啟用\\ "
":guilabel:`重新導向舊網址`\\ 時，系統會自動加入重新導向記錄。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:170
msgid ""
"You can set up redirections for :ref:`static and dynamic pages <website/"
"pages/page_type>`."
msgstr "您可以為\\ :ref:`靜態和動態頁面 <website/pages/page_type>`\\ 設定重新導向。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:172
msgid ""
"To create a new redirection, click the :guilabel:`New` button, then fill in "
"the fields:"
msgstr "若要建立新的重新導向，請按一下\\ :guilabel:`新增`\\ 按鈕，然後填寫欄位："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:174
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: Enter a name to identify the redirect."
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`名稱`\\ ：輸入名稱以識別該重新導向。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:175
msgid ":guilabel:`Action`: Select the type of redirection:"
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`動作`\\ ：選擇重新導向的類型："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`404 Not found`: visitors are redirected to a 404 error page when "
"they try to access an unpublished or deleted page."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`404 找不到`\\ ：當訪客嘗試存取未發佈或已刪除的頁面時，會被重新"
"導向至 404 錯誤頁面。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:179
msgid ""
":guilabel:`301 Moved Permanently`: for permanent redirections of unpublished "
"or deleted :ref:`static pages <website/pages/page_type>`. The new URL is "
"shown in search engine results, and the redirect is cached by browsers."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`301 永久移動`\\ ：用於未發佈或已刪除之\\ :ref:`靜態頁面 "
"<website/pages/page_type>`\\ 的永久重新導向。新網址會顯示在搜尋引擎結果中，且"
"重新導向會被瀏覽器快取。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:182
msgid ""
":guilabel:`302 Moved Temporarily`: for short-term redirections, for example, "
"if you are redesigning or updating a page. The new URL is neither cached by "
"browsers nor shown in search engine results."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`302 暫時移動`\\ ：用於短期重新導向，例如當您正在重新設計或更新"
"頁面時。新網址不會被瀏覽器快取，也不會顯示在搜尋引擎結果中。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:185
msgid ""
":guilabel:`308 Redirect/Rewrite`: for permanent redirections of "
"existing :ref:`dynamic pages <website/pages/page_type>`. The URL is renamed; "
"the new name is shown in search engine results and is cached by browsers. "
"Use this redirect type to rename a dynamic page, for example, if you wish to "
"rename `/shop` into `/market`."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`308 重新導向/重寫`\\ ：用於現有\\ :ref:`動態頁面 <website/"
"pages/page_type>`\\ 的永久重新導向。網址會重新命名；新名稱會顯示在搜尋引擎結"
"果中，且會被瀏覽器快取。使用此重新導向類型來重新命名動態頁面，例如若您希望將 "
"`/shop` 重新命名為 `/market`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL from`: Enter the URL to be redirected (e.g., `/about-the-"
"company`) or search for the desired :ref:`dynamic page <website/pages/"
"page_type>` and select it from the list."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`來源網址`\\ ：輸入要重新導向的網址（例如\\ `/about-the-"
"company`）或搜尋所需的\\ :ref:`動態頁面 <website/pages/page_type>`\\ 並從清單"
"中選取。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:192
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL to`: For 301, 302, and 308 redirects, enter the URL to be "
"redirected to. If you want to redirect to an external URL, include the "
"protocol (e.g., `https://`)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`目標網址`\\ ：對於 301、302 和 308 重新導向，輸入要重新導向至的"
"網址。如果您要重新導向至外部網址，請包含通訊協定（例如\\ `https://`）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:194
msgid ":guilabel:`Website`: Select a specific website."
msgstr "\\ :guilabel:`網站`\\ ：選擇特定網站。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:195
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sequence`: To define the order in which redirections are "
"performed, e.g., in the case of redirect chains (i.e., a series of redirects "
"where one URL is redirected to another one, which is itself further "
"redirected to another URL)."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`順序`\\ ：用於定義執行重新導向的順序，例如在重新導向鏈的情況下"
"（即一系列重新導向，其中一個網址被重新導向至另一個網址,而該網址本身又被進一步"
"重新導向至另一個網址）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:199
msgid "Toggle the :guilabel:`Activate` switch to deactivate the redirection."
msgstr "切換\\ :guilabel:`啟用`\\ 開關以停用重新導向。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:202
msgid ""
"404, 301, and 302 redirections are meant to migrate traffic "
"from :ref:`unpublished <website/pages/un-publish-page>` or :ref:`deleted "
"<website/pages/delete-page>` pages to *new* pages, while the 308 redirect is "
"used for *permanent* redirections of *existing* pages."
msgstr ""
"404、301 和 302 重新導向用於將流量從\\ :ref:`未發佈 <website/pages/un-"
"publish-page>`\\ 或\\ :ref:`已刪除 <website/pages/delete-page>`\\ 的頁面遷移"
"至\\ *新*\\ 頁面，而 308 重新導向則用於\\ *現有*\\ 頁面的\\ *永久*\\ 重新導向"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:207
msgid ""
"`Google documentation on redirects and search <https://developers.google.com/"
"search/docs/crawling-indexing/301-redirects>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Google 關於重新導向與搜尋的使用說明\\ <https://developers.google.com/search/"
"docs/crawling-indexing/301-redirects>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:208
msgid ":doc:`seo`"
msgstr ":doc:`seo`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:5
msgid ""
"Search Engine Optimization, often abbreviated as SEO, is a digital marketing "
"strategy to improve a website's visibility and ranking in search engine "
"results (e.g., in Google). It involves optimizing various elements on your "
"website, including its content, social sharing, URLs, images, and page speed."
msgstr ""
"搜尋引擎最佳化（通常簡稱為 SEO）是一種數位行銷策略，用於提升網站在搜尋引擎結"
"果（例如 Google）中的可見度和排名。它涉及最佳化網站上的各種元素，包括內容、社"
"群分享、網址、圖片和頁面速度。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:11
msgid ""
"Odoo provides several modules to help you build your website content, such "
"as :doc:`eCommerce <../../ecommerce>`, :doc:`Blog <../../"
"blog>`, :doc:`eLearning <../../elearning>`, and :doc:`Forum <../../forum>`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 提供多個模組來協助您建立網站內容，例如\\ :doc:`電子商務 <../../"
"ecommerce>`\\ 、\\ :doc:`部落格 <../../blog>`\\ 、\\ :doc:`網上學習 <../../"
"elearning>`\\ 和\\ :doc:`論壇 <../../forum>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:14
msgid ""
"All Odoo :doc:`themes <../web_design/themes>` rely on the CSS Framework "
"`Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com/>`_ to render efficiently according to "
"the device: desktop, tablet, or mobile, which positively impacts ranking in "
"search engines."
msgstr ""
"所有 Odoo\\ :doc:`佈景主題 <../web_design/themes>`\\ 都依賴 CSS 框架 "
"`Bootstrap <https://getbootstrap.com/>`_ 來根據裝置（桌面、平板或行動裝置）有"
"效呈現，這對搜尋引擎的排名有正面影響。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:19
msgid ""
"`Magic Sheet - Optimize your website [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/"
"folders/1Ywip4tWF2DPkcBaEbeXJxIZg2CjkwKgb>`_"
msgstr ""
"`精妙筆記 - 優化網站設定 [PDF] <https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/"
"1Ywip4tWF2DPkcBaEbeXJxIZg2CjkwKgb>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:23
msgid "Content optimization"
msgstr "內容最佳化"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:25
msgid ""
"To optimize a webpage's SEO, access the page, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Optimize SEO`."
msgstr ""
"若要最佳化網頁的 SEO，請存取該頁面，然後前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 網"
"站 --> 最佳化 SEO`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:None
msgid "Optimize SEO"
msgstr "SEO 最佳化"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:32
msgid ""
"If you change the title of a blog post or the name of a product, the link to "
"the related webpage is automatically updated. The old link still functions "
"as Odoo creates a :ref:`301 redirect <website/pages/URL-redirection>`, "
"maintaining the SEO."
msgstr ""
"如果您變更部落格文章的標題或產品名稱，相關網頁的連結會自動更新。舊連結仍然有"
"效，因為 Odoo 會建立\\ :ref:`301 重新導向 <website/pages/URL-redirection>`\\ "
"，維持 SEO。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:37
msgid "Keywords and Meta tags"
msgstr "關鍵字和 Meta 標籤"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:39
msgid "There are two types of keywords in SEO, which serve different purposes."
msgstr "SEO 中有兩種類型的關鍵字，它們的用途不同。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:42
msgid "In-text keywords"
msgstr "文內關鍵字"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:44
msgid ""
"In-text keywords appear naturally throughout a page’s visible content "
"(titles, headings, and body text) and help search engines determine the "
"topic and relevance of the page. These keywords have a real impact on "
"ranking. They cannot be edited in the :guilabel:`optimize SEO` pop-up."
msgstr ""
"文內關鍵字會自然地出現在頁面的可見內容（標題、標頭和正文）中，有助於搜尋引擎"
"判斷頁面的主題和相關性。這些關鍵字對排名有實際影響。它們無法在\\ "
":guilabel:`最佳化 SEO`\\ 彈出視窗中進行編輯。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:49
msgid "It is strongly recommended to only use one H1 title per page for SEO."
msgstr "強烈建議每個頁面僅使用一個 H1 標題，以利於 SEO。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:52
msgid "Meta tags and meta keywords"
msgstr "中繼標籤和中繼關鍵字"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Meta tags** are HTML elements that provide information about a webpage to "
"search engines and website visitors. They play a crucial role in SEO by "
"helping search engines understand the content and context of a webpage and "
"attract visitors with appealing content. They can be edited in "
"the :guilabel:`optimize SEO` pop-up. There are two types of meta tags in "
"Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"**中繼標籤**是 HTML 元素，可向搜尋引擎和網站訪客提供網頁資訊。它們在 SEO 中扮"
"演關鍵角色，幫助搜尋引擎理解網頁的內容和脈絡，並以吸引人的內容吸引訪客。可"
"在\\ :guilabel:`最佳化 SEO`\\ 彈出視窗中編輯。Odoo 中有兩種類型的中繼標籤："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:59
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Title` tags specify a webpage's title and are displayed as a "
"clickable link in search engine results. They should be concise, "
"descriptive, and relevant to the page's content. You can update the title "
"tag of your webpage or keep it empty to use the default value based on the "
"page’s content."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`標題`\\ 標籤指定網頁的標題，並在搜尋引擎結果中顯示為可點擊的連結。"
"標題應簡潔、具描述性且與頁面內容相關。您可以更新網頁的標題標籤，或保持空白以"
"使用基於頁面內容的預設值。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description` tags summarize the webpage's content, often "
"displayed in search engine results below the title. They are used to "
"encourage the user to visit the page. You can update the description tag of "
"your webpage or keep it empty to use the default value based on the page’s "
"content."
msgstr ""
"\\ :guilabel:`Description`\\ 標籤會摘要網頁的內容，通常會在搜尋引擎結果中顯示"
"於標題下方。它們用於鼓勵使用者造訪該頁面。您可以更新網頁的 description 標籤，"
"或將其保持為空以使用根據頁面內容產生的預設值。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:70
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Preview` card displays how the title and description tags "
"should appear in search results. It also includes the URL of your page."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`預覽`\\ 卡片顯示標題和描述標籤在搜尋結果中的呈現方式。它還包含您頁"
"面的網址。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:73
msgid ""
"**Meta keywords** are placed in a hidden HTML tag `<meta "
"name=\"keywords\">`. Once used to describe a page’s topic, this tag is now "
"ignored by major search engines and has little or no impact on SEO. To "
"edit :guilabel:`Keywords`, enter the keywords you consider essential in this "
"field and click :guilabel:`Add` to see how they are used at different levels "
"in your content (H1, H2, page title, page description, page content) and the "
"related searches in Google. The tool also suggests relevant keywords."
msgstr ""
"**中繼關鍵字**會放在隱藏的 HTML 標籤「<meta name=\"keywords\">」中。此標籤曾"
"用於描述頁面的主題，但現在主要搜尋引擎已忽略它，對 SEO 的影響很小或沒有影響。"
"若要編輯\\ :guilabel:`關鍵字`\\ ，請在此欄位中輸入您認為必要的關鍵字，然後按"
"一下\\ :guilabel:`加入`\\ ，以查看它們在內容的不同層級（H1、H2、頁面標題、頁"
"面說明、頁面內容）中如何使用，以及 Google 中的相關搜尋。該工具也會建議相關的"
"關鍵字。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design/elements.rst:64
msgid "Images"
msgstr "圖片"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:83
msgid ""
"The size of images has a significant impact on page speed, which is an "
"essential criterion for search engines to optimize SEO ranking."
msgstr "圖片大小對頁面速度有顯著影響，而頁面速度是搜尋引擎最佳化 SEO 排名的重要標準。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:87
msgid ""
"Compare how your website ranks using `Google Page Speed <https://"
"pagespeed.web.dev/?utm_source=psi&utm_medium=redirect>`_ or `Pingdom Website "
"Speed Test <https://tools.pingdom.com/>`_."
msgstr ""
"使用\\ `Google Page Speed <https://pagespeed.web.dev/"
"?utm_source=psi&utm_medium=redirect>`_\\ 或\\ `Pingdom Website Speed Test "
"<https://tools.pingdom.com/>`_\\ 比較您網站的排名。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:90
msgid ""
"Odoo automatically compresses uploaded images and converts them to `Webp`. "
"With this file format, photos are smaller, which increases the page loading "
"speed and, therefore, gives a better ranking in SEO. All images used in Odoo "
"official :doc:`themes <../web_design/themes>` are also compressed by "
"default. If you are using a third-party theme, it may provide images that "
"are not compressed efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 會自動壓縮上傳的圖片並將其轉換為 `Webp`。使用這種檔案格式，照片會更小，"
"從而提升頁面載入速度，因此能在 SEO 中獲得更好的排名。Odoo 官方\\ :doc:`佈景主"
"題 <../web_design/themes>`\\ 中使用的所有圖片預設也都經過壓縮。如果您使用的是"
"第三方佈景主題，它可能會提供未經有效壓縮的圖片。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:96
msgid ""
"**To modify an image** from your website, select the image, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit`, then go to the :guilabel:`Customize` tab, and adapt "
"the :guilabel:`Format` in the :guilabel:`Image` section."
msgstr ""
"**若要修改網站上的圖片**，請選取該圖片，按一下\\ :guilabel:`Edit`\\ ，然後前"
"往\\ :guilabel:`Customize`\\ 分頁，並在\\ :guilabel:`Image`\\ 區段中調整\\ "
":guilabel:`Format`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:100
msgid ""
"Alt tags are used to provide context to what an image is displaying, "
"informing search engine crawlers and allowing them to index an image "
"correctly. Adding alt tags keywords in the :guilabel:`Description` field is "
"essential from an SEO perspective. This description is added to the HTML "
"code of your image, and it is shown when the image cannot be displayed."
msgstr ""
"替代文字標籤用於提供圖片顯示內容的背景資訊，告知搜尋引擎爬蟲並讓它們能夠正確"
"索引圖片。從 SEO 角度來看，在\\ :guilabel:`描述`\\ 欄位中加入替代文字關鍵字至"
"關重要。此描述會加入到圖片的 HTML 程式碼中，並在圖片無法顯示時顯示。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:106
msgid "Image for social share"
msgstr "社群分享圖片"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:108
msgid ""
"When you share your page on social media, your website logo is selected by "
"default, but you can search the :doc:`Unsplash image library <../../../"
"general/integrations/unsplash>` or upload any other image by clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-upload` :guilabel:`(upload)` button."
msgstr ""
"當您在社交媒體上分享頁面時，預設會選擇您的網站標誌，但您可以搜尋\\ "
":doc:`Unsplash 圖片圖書館 <../../../general/integrations/unsplash>`\\ 或按一"
"下\\ :icon:`fa-upload`\\ :guilabel:`上傳`\\ 按鈕上傳任何其他圖片。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:113
msgid ""
"You can set a default social share image. Go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` in the :guilabel:`SEO` section and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Default Social Share Image` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"您可以設定預設的社交分享圖片。前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 配置 --> 設"
"定`\\ 中的\\ :guilabel:`SEO`\\ 區段，並勾選\\ :guilabel:`預設社交分享圖片`\\ "
"勾選方格。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:117
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Social Preview` card displays how the page's information "
"would appear when shared."
msgstr ":guilabel:`社群預覽`\\ 卡片顯示頁面資訊在分享時的呈現方式。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:121
msgid "Indexation"
msgstr "索引"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:123
msgid ""
"Website indexation is the process by which search engines, such as Google, "
"discover, analyze, and store information about a website's content in their "
"database. Search engine bots, known as crawlers or spiders, visit web pages "
"and follow links to collect data, including text, images, and other media. "
"The purpose of indexation is to make a website's content searchable and "
"discoverable to users. Without being indexed, a website or a specific page "
"on that site will not appear in search engine results, regardless of how "
"relevant or well-designed it is. Indexation is a fundamental step "
"in :abbr:`SEO (Search Engine Optimization)`, serving as the foundation for a "
"website's visibility and organic traffic."
msgstr ""
"網站索引是搜尋引擎（例如 Google）探索、分析並將網站內容資訊儲存在其資料庫中的"
"過程。稱為爬蟲或蜘蛛的搜尋引擎機器人會造訪網頁並跟隨連結來收集資料，包括文字"
"、圖片和其他媒體。索引的目的是使網站的內容可供使用者搜尋和探索。如果沒有被索"
"引，無論網站或該網站上的特定頁面有多相關或設計得多好，都不會出現在搜尋引擎結"
"果中。索引是\\ :abbr:`SEO（搜尋引擎最佳化）`\\ 的基本步驟，是網站能見度和自然"
"流量的基礎。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:133
msgid ""
"**When you first create your website on Odoo, it will not appear directly in "
"search engine results.** Search engines need time to crawl and index it, "
"which can take anywhere from a few days to several weeks. For Google, you "
"can use the :doc:`Search Console <../configuration/google_search_console>` "
"and request indexing for specific URLs, though this does not guarantee "
"faster results. If you have an existing website and are migrating, your "
"previous website may still appear instead of the new one during that "
"timeframe."
msgstr ""
"**當您首次在 Odoo 上建立網站時，它不會直接出現在搜尋引擎結果中。**搜尋引擎需"
"要時間來爬取和索引它，這可能需要幾天到幾週的時間。對於 Google，您可以使用\\ "
":doc:`Search Console <../configuration/google_search_console>`\\ 並請求為特定"
"網址建立索引，但這並不能保證更快的結果。如果您有現有網站並正在遷移，則在該時"
"間範圍內，您以前的網站可能仍會顯示，而不是新網站。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:141
msgid "SEO impact when migrating your existing website to Odoo"
msgstr "將現有網站遷移到 Odoo 時的 SEO 影響"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:143
msgid ""
"In most cases, migrating to Odoo will not negatively impact your SEO. While "
"no platform can guarantee that rankings will remain unchanged, follow these "
"best practices to significantly reduce the risk."
msgstr ""
"在大多數情況下，遷移到 Odoo 不會對您的 SEO 產生負面影響。雖然沒有平台可以保證"
"排名保持不變，但遵循這些最佳實務可以顯著降低風險。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:147
msgid "Keep your existing content."
msgstr "保留現有內容。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:149
msgid ""
"Implement :ref:`redirects <website/pages/URL-redirection>` from old URLs to "
"their new counterparts."
msgstr "實施從舊\\ :ref:`網址 <website/pages/URL-redirection>`\\ 到新網址的重新導向。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:151
msgid ""
"Monitor traffic and indexation to make sure that everything is going well, "
"using :doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`."
msgstr ""
"使用\\ :doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`\\ 監控流量和索引狀態，確"
"保一切正常運作。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:153
msgid ""
"By doing this, you help search engines reindex your site and maintain your "
"visibility in search results."
msgstr "這樣做可以幫助搜尋引擎重新索引您的網站，並維持您在搜尋結果中的可見度。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:157
msgid "It is normal to experience a traffic decrease in the first days."
msgstr "在最初幾天內流量下降是正常現象。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:160
msgid "Prevent a page from being indexed"
msgstr "防止頁面被索引"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:162
msgid ""
"To effectively prevent a page from appearing in search engine results, use "
"one of the following methods:"
msgstr "要有效防止頁面出現在搜尋引擎結果中，請使用以下其中一種方法："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:165
msgid ""
"**noindex tag:** Access the page's :ref:`properties <website/pages/"
"page_properties>` and toggle the :guilabel:`Indexed` switch off."
msgstr ""
"**noindex 標籤：**存取頁面的\\ :ref:`屬性 <website/pages/page_properties>`\\ "
"，並將\\ :guilabel:`已索引`\\ 開關切換為關閉。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:169
msgid ""
"This option is not yet available for :ref:`dynamic pages <website/pages/"
"page_type>`."
msgstr "此選項目前尚不適用於\\ :ref:`動態頁面 <website/pages/page_type>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:171
msgid ""
"**404 or 403:** Configure the page to return a 404 (Not Found) or 403 "
"(Forbidden) HTTP status code. These codes signal to search engines that the "
"page does not exist or is inaccessible, leading to its eventual removal from "
"the index."
msgstr ""
"**404 或 403：**將頁面配置為傳回 404（找不到）或 403（禁止存取）HTTP 狀態碼。"
"這些代碼會向搜尋引擎發出訊號，表示頁面不存在或無法存取，最終導致其從索引中移"
"除。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:175
msgid ""
"**404:** :ref:`Configure a 404 redirection. <website/pages/URL-redirection>`"
msgstr "**404：**\\ :ref:`配置 404 重新導向 <website/pages/URL-redirection>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:176
msgid ""
"**403:** Access the page's :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_properties>` "
"and toggle the :guilabel:`Visibility` switch off or :ref:`unpublish the page "
"<website/pages/un-publish-page>`."
msgstr ""
"**403：**存取頁面的\\ :ref:`屬性 <website/pages/page_properties>`\\ ，並將\\ "
":guilabel:`可見性`\\ 開關切換為關閉，或\\ :ref:`取消發布頁面 <website/pages/"
"un-publish-page>`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:179
msgid ""
"**Google Search Console:** Use Google Search Console to request the removal "
"of specific URLs from Google's index."
msgstr ""
"**Google Search Console：**使用 Google Search Console 請求從 Google 索引中移"
"除特定網址。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:183
msgid ":doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`"
msgstr ":doc:`../configuration/google_search_console`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:184
msgid ":doc:`pages`"
msgstr ":doc:`pages`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:187
msgid "Prevent a website from being indexed"
msgstr "防止網站被索引"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:189
msgid ""
"To prevent a website from appearing in search engine results, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`, then in "
"the :guilabel:`Website Info` section, add a random value in "
"the :guilabel:`Domain` field. Doing so automatically inserts the following "
"tag into the page source:"
msgstr ""
"若要防止網站出現在搜尋引擎結果中，請前往\\ :menuselection:`配置 --> 設定`\\ "
"，然後在\\ :guilabel:`網站資訊`\\ 區段的\\ :guilabel:`網域`\\ 欄位中加入隨機"
"值。這樣做會自動在頁面原始碼中插入以下標籤："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:198
msgid ""
"This tag instructs search engines not to index the site. After applying the "
"change, it may take several days or weeks for search engines to update their "
"results and remove the website."
msgstr ""
"此標籤會指示搜尋引擎不要索引該網站。套用變更後，搜尋引擎可能需要數天或數週的"
"時間來更新其結果並移除該網站。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:202
msgid ""
"This can be used to prevent websites from test databases from appearing in "
"search results."
msgstr "這可用於防止測試資料庫的網站出現在搜尋結果中。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:205
msgid "Sitemap"
msgstr "網站地圖"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:207
msgid ""
"The sitemap points out website pages and their relation to each other to "
"search engine crawlers. Odoo generates a `/sitemap.xml` file, including all "
"URLs. For performance reasons, this file is cached and updated every 12 "
"hours."
msgstr ""
"網站地圖會向搜尋引擎檢索器指出網站頁面及其相互關係。Odoo 會產生包含所有網址"
"的\\ `/sitemap.xml`\\ 檔案。基於效能考量，此檔案會被快取並每 12 小時更新一次"
"。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:212
msgid ""
"If your website has a lot of pages, Odoo automatically creates a Sitemap "
"Index file, respecting the `sitemaps.org protocol <http://www.sitemaps.org/"
"protocol.html>`_, grouping sitemap URLs in 45000 chunks per file."
msgstr ""
"如果您的網站有大量頁面，Odoo 會自動建立網站地圖索引檔案，遵循 `sitemaps.org "
"協定 <http://www.sitemaps.org/protocol.html>`_，將網站地圖網址分組為每個檔案 "
"45000 個區塊。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:216
msgid ""
"Every sitemap entry has three attributes that are computed automatically:"
msgstr "每個網站地圖記項都有三個自動計算的屬性："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:218
msgid "`<loc>`: the URL of a page."
msgstr "`<loc>`：頁面的網址。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:219
msgid ""
"`<lastmod>`: last modification date of the resource, computed automatically "
"based on the related object. For a page related to a product, this could be "
"the last modification date of the product or the page."
msgstr ""
"`<lastmod>`：資源的最後修改日期，根據相關物件自動計算。對於與產品相關的頁面，"
"這可能是產品或頁面的最後修改日期。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:222
msgid ""
"`<priority>`: modules may implement their priority algorithm based on their "
"content (for example, a forum might assign a priority based on the number of "
"votes on a specific post). The priority of a static page is defined by its "
"priority field, which is normalized (16 is the default)."
msgstr ""
"`<priority>`：模組可能會根據其內容實作自己的優先順序演算法（例如，論壇可能會"
"根據特定貼文的投票數來分配優先順序）。靜態頁面的優先順序由其優先順序欄位定義"
"，該欄位已標準化（預設為 16）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:227
msgid ""
"To prevent pages from appearing in a sitemap, go to :menuselection:`Site --> "
"Properties`, and toggle off the :guilabel:`Indexed` feature."
msgstr ""
"若要防止頁面出現在網站地圖中，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 屬性`\\ ，並"
"關閉\\ :guilabel:`已索引`\\ 功能。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:0
msgid "toggle off the “Indexed” field"
msgstr "關閉「已索引」欄位"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:234
msgid "robots.txt"
msgstr "robots.txt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:236
msgid ""
"A `robots.txt` file instructs search engine crawlers which parts of a "
"website they are permitted to access. Its primary purpose is to:"
msgstr "`robots.txt`\\ 檔案指示搜尋引擎爬蟲可以存取網站的哪些部分。其主要目的是："

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:239
msgid ""
"**Prevent overloading the website:** By guiding crawlers away from certain "
"sections, robots.txt helps manage server load."
msgstr "**防止網站超載：**透過引導爬蟲遠離某些區段，robots.txt 有助於管理伺服器負載。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:241
msgid ""
"**Control access to resources and detailed descriptions:** It can prevent "
"crawlers from accessing media files (images, videos), CSS stylesheets, and "
"JavaScript files, and from reading the content (text) of specific pages."
msgstr ""
"**控制資源和詳細描述的存取：**它可以防止爬蟲存取媒體檔案（圖片、影片）、CSS "
"樣式表和 JavaScript 檔案，以及讀取特定頁面的內容（文字）。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:245
msgid ""
"When indexing your website, search engines first look at the robots.txt "
"file. Odoo automatically creates one robot.txt file available on "
"`mydatabase.odoo.com/robots.txt`."
msgstr ""
"搜尋引擎在索引您的網站時，會先查看 robots.txt 檔案。Odoo 會自動建立一個可在\\"
" `mydatabase.odoo.com/robots.txt`\\ 取得的 robots.txt 檔案。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:249
msgid ""
"Reputable bots adhere to robots.txt; others may require blocking "
"via :ref:`Cloudflare <domain-name/naked/cloudflare>` on your custom domain."
msgstr ""
"信譽良好的機器人會遵守 robots.txt；其他機器人可能需要透過自訂網域上的\\ "
":ref:`Cloudflare <domain-name/naked/cloudflare>`\\ 進行封鎖。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:253
msgid "Edit robots.txt"
msgstr "編輯 robots.txt"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:255
msgid ""
"By editing a robots.txt file, you can control which site pages are "
"accessible to search engine crawlers. To add custom instructions to the "
"file, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll "
"down to the :guilabel:`SEO` section, and click :guilabel:`Edit robots.txt`."
msgstr ""
"透過編輯 robots.txt 檔案，您可以控制搜尋引擎爬蟲可以存取哪些網站頁面。要在檔"
"案中加入自訂指令，請前往\\ :menuselection:`網站 --> 配置 --> 設定`\\ ，向下捲"
"動到\\ :guilabel:`SEO`\\ 區段，然後按一下\\ :guilabel:`編輯 robots.txt`\\ 。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:260
msgid ""
"If you do not want robots to crawl the `/about-us` page of your site, you "
"can edit the robots.txt file to add `Disallow: /about-us`."
msgstr ""
"如果您不希望機器人爬取網站的 `/about-us` 頁面，可以編輯 robots.txt 檔案並加"
"入 `Disallow: /about-us`。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:264
msgid ""
"While `robots.txt` prevents content from being crawled, **it does not "
"guarantee that a page will not be indexed**. A page can still appear in "
"search results if it is linked to from other crawled pages (indexed by "
"\"reference\"). Google generally does not recommend using robots.txt to "
"block webpages that you wish to keep out of search results entirely."
msgstr ""
"雖然 `robots.txt` 可以防止內容被爬取，**但它無法保證頁面不會被索引**。如果其"
"他已爬取的頁面有連結指向該頁面，該頁面仍可能出現在搜尋結果中（透過「參照」建"
"立索引）。Google 通常不建議使用 robots.txt 來封鎖您希望完全排除在搜尋結果之外"
"的網頁。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:270
msgid "Advanced features"
msgstr "進階功能，幫你蒐集有用資訊"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:273
msgid "Structured data markup"
msgstr "結構化資料標記"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:275
msgid ""
"Structured data markup is used to generate rich snippets in search engine "
"results. It is a way for websites to send structured data to search engine "
"crawlers, helping them understand your content and create well-presented "
"search results."
msgstr ""
"結構化資料標記用於在搜尋引擎結果中產生豐富的摘要資訊。這是網站向搜尋引擎檢索"
"器傳送結構化資料的方式，幫助它們理解您的內容並建立精美的搜尋結果。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:279
msgid ""
"By default, Google supports many `rich snippets <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/blog/2009/05/introducing-rich-snippets>`_ for "
"content types, including Reviews, People, Products, Businesses, Events, and "
"Organizations."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，Google 支援多種內容類型的\\ `豐富摘要 <https://"
"developers.google.com/search/blog/2009/05/introducing-rich-snippets>`_\\ ，包"
"括評論、人物、產品、企業、活動和組織。"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/seo.rst:282
msgid ""
"Microdata is a set of tags, introduced with HTML5, that help search engines "
"better understand your content and display it in a relevant way. Odoo "
"implements microdata as defined in the schema.org `specification <https://"
"schema.org/docs/gs.html>`_ for events, eCommerce products, forum posts, and "
"contact addresses. This allows your product pages to be displayed in Google "
"using extra information like the price and rating of a product:"
msgstr ""
"微資料是一組隨 HTML5 引入的標籤，可幫助搜尋引擎更好地理解您的內容並以相關方式"
